17.title: Mistaken Identity
17.plot: How many times has this happened to you; you're out and about and someone begins talking to you in a language you just can't understand because they thought you were their same ethnicity?!! I know it's happened to us too many times. Here's a day in the life of KT Tatara, a regular dude who is mistaken for a Chinese food delivery dude, a Mexican, and a lesbian... OUCH! How'd you feel if you were a dude and two hotties thought you're a female? Think you would have done what he did?

18.title: Extreme Safety League
18.plot: Meet Brad and Chad leaders of "E.S.L" (which stands for Extreme Safety League), they go from skateboards, to bikes, to snowboards teaching the world that being EXTREMELY safe is the ultimate cool, but the rest of the world begs to differ. They are so so so safe that they end up putting themselves in really dangerous situations and ultimately sound like big baby douche bags. Being safe is ALWAYS cool, but being judgmental because your scared of what you don't understand is never a good look.

19.title: Secrets
19.plot: We all know how juicy secrets are. Once you hear one, you can't wait to pass it on. But, secrets are meant to be kept because they're given to you based on trust. So make sure you don't break that trust and wear a condom.

20.title: Nerd Love
20.plot: Most of the time what's holding you back from getting the girl or guy you want is you. Stop placing imaginary barriers between yourself and the person you like. Just shut up and talk to them, but don't be a creeper.

21.title: Crazy Asian Parent: Sex Ed
21.plot: Crazy Asian Dad and Mom can't wait for their son to get lucky with his cute study buddy. Too bad homeboy is way too shy and gentlemanly for his own good. No worries though, Crazy Asian Parents are there to try and make the magic happen. Freaky deeky, horny release.

22.title: Baby Sluts
22.plot: Nowadays, youngins are starting to have sex earlier and earlier. Witness how these slutty babies pass around STDs to each other on the playground as well as other consequences of having unsafe sex. Learn from the mistakes of others, babies. Put a glove on it before you love on it.

23.title: Homie Love
23.plot: Girls dig a guy who can be comfortable with his sexuality. So why can't a guy tell his homie that he be lookin' cute and all?

24.title: Justin Bieber 'Die in Your Arms' Parody: Lie in Your Barn
24.plot: It's tough being a barn animal when you're always forced to be out in the fields without any luxuries. Animals need vacations too! Check out these poor barn animals and their plea to just "Lie In Your Barn." Enjoy Justkiddingfilms' take on Justin Bieber's hot new single "Die In Your Arms."

25.title: You Know You're Asian If - Part 1
25.plot: Looks like there's more Asian in you than you thought huh? Guess we all got an Asian mom inside of us. Let us know about the Asian inside of you in the comments and we'll include it in the next one.

26.title: Making the Bus Monitor Cry - Response
26.plot: Just Kidding Films' response to the "Making The Bus Monitor Cry" video.

27.title: Sexy Asian Model
27.plot: In the entertainment world where Asians are seen as a minority group, we all need to stick together to succeed. Confucious say, don't be selfish and help a brotha out.

28.title: Korean Men Fight Over Video Game
28.plot:
Know what this is about?
 Be the first one to add a plot.

29.title: Kanye West 'Mercy' Parody: Mazda
29.plot: Kanye's "Mercy" is a dope track, but we ain't fancy enough to relate to that stuff. This parody keeps it real because you don't need a Lamborghini to appreciate your ride. If it's got wheels and gets you from one place to another, you're good to go.

30.title: You Know You're Asian If - Part 2
30.plot: Back by popular demand! Looks like there's more Asian in you than you thought huh? Guess we all got an Asian mom inside of us. Let us know about the Asian inside of you in the comments.

31.title: Student Life
31.plot: We've all been there; the tests, the homework, the classes, the detentions. There's a universal understanding among all students that sometimes school can be a real burden. Luckily, you're not alone.

32.title: Gossip Girls
32.plot: Don't you just hate how passive aggressive some people are? Instead of being fake and making yourself and others around you miserable, just be real and upfront. Save the drama for your mama.

33.title: Childhood Bully
33.plot: Everyone's been bullied in some form or another at least once in their life. Revenge is never the answer, it only perpetuates the violence and you end up being the angel bitch to the bully God.

34.title: Guys Vs Girls: Stories
34.plot: Did you ever notice that guys and girls have a very different way of communicating thoughts, especially when it comes to story-telling? Guys tend to focus on the story so much that they embellish the details. And girls have trouble sticking to the story while going off on random tangents. However, at the end of the day we still get two very interesting stories.

35.title: Jeremy Lin Is Korean
35.plot: Jeremy Lin is Korean. Basketball is a Korean and Jesus collaboration invention.

36.title: Adopted
36.plot: Crazy Asian Mom and Dad have to break the news to their sons Tim and Rick that one of them is adopted. No worries though, they've also found the real dad! However, things aren't always as they seem.

37.title: PSY: Gangnam Style M/V - Parody
37.plot: Handsome Style VS. Nuoc Mam Style? It doesn't matter! Whether you're Korean or Vietnamese or any other Asian, no one's going to care once they see you bust a move. JK style!

38.title: Bad Memory
38.plot: Having forgetful friends is like being friends with the lady from The Notebook. They can never remember sh*t you tell them but you can't stay mad at them because their intentions are good.

39.title: Why Is Cussing Wrong?
39.plot: Why is cussing such a big deal? Let's face it, it sounds ridiculous and unnatural when you tone it down anyway. Might as well go all the way because cussing doesn't make you a bad person, having bad intent does.

40.title: Six Pack Short Cuts Parody
40.plot: The Six Pack Shortcuts System really works! Definitely check out and support our buddies over at sixpackshortcuts.

41.title: Twilight Sucks
41.plot: What's with the sparkly supermodel vampires of today? Let's demand pop culture to give us back our terrifying and creepy vampires that we grew up having nightmares about.

42.title: Guys Vs Girl: Communication
42.plot: Let's face it we know Guys and Girls speak two different languages. Let's not focus on which way is better but how we can help understand each other.

43.title: Friend Problems
43.plot: Yes, we know good friends care and voice our opinions to help out. But, its important that our opinions to stay opinions and not become commands. Because, its more important that our friends live their own lives and learn on their own.

44.title: Why Parents Criticise
44.plot: Some parents don't know any other way to show their love except by yelling and criticizing. We can't blame their "tough-lovin ways" cause that's how they were raised. But, relationships are a two way street. Its up to us to show them old grass hoppers a thing or two about positive reinforcement.

45.title: Losing Stuff
45.plot: One minute you have it, one minute you don't. Losing stuff is as annoying as it is funny because it's usually the result of day dreaming or brain farting.

46.title: Worst Movie Death Scene Ever!
46.plot:
Know what this is about?
 Be the first one to add a plot.

47.title: I'd Rather Have a Dog Than a Girlfriend
47.plot: Girlfriends are nice and all, but when I compare the perks between having a dog or girl friend, having a dog outshines having a girlfriend like crazy. Anyone else feel the same?

48.title: Special Message
48.plot: Joe has his first experience of a full body massage. He expects the parlor to be full of beautiful women ready to pleasure his special needs, but to his surprise, reality is far from his imaginations.

49.title: Asian Discipline
49.plot: Asian moms are the best discipliner's, they are so good they should be part of the correctional system. Criminals would get rehabilitated by a swift Asian mom ass beating followed by homework in arithmetic, English, and history. Don't ever mess with Asian moms, they look little but they can pack a punch.
